# Welcome to the Help Website

This website was created as a resource for our classmates. All of the original instructions and helpful content remain in place—simply update or add new sections as needed.

## Getting Started

Here you’ll find tutorials, guides, and tips to help you with your coursework and projects.

## Additional Information

- [Meet the Team!](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/degrees/master-of-financial-engineering/meet-our-team-overview)
- **Contact:** mfe@anderson.ucla.edu 
- **Office:** UCLA Anderson Room C401

## Academic Resources {#academic-resources}

:::{.ucla-accent}
Access course materials, study spaces, and academic support to excel in your program.
:::

### Course Materials
- [UCLA Library](https://www.library.ucla.edu/) - Access textbooks and course materials
- [UCLA BruinLearn](https://bruinlearn.ucla.edu/) - UCLA's Coursework Program (also known as Canvas)
- [Anderson Course Catalog](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/degrees/master-of-financial-engineering/academics) - Browse MFE Courses

### Study Spaces
- [UCLA Study Room Reservations](https://www.asucla.ucla.edu/ucla/ucla-study-room-reservation) - Library study rooms for reservation
- [Anderson Study Rooms](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/rosenfeld-library) - Reservation for study rooms can be made at the front desk

### Tutoring and Academic Support
- Look for some

## Financial Information {#financial-information}

:::{.ucla-accent}
Navigate tuition, fees, financial aid, and employment opportunities with these essential resources.
:::

### Tuition and Fees
- [MFE Program Costs](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/degrees/master-of-financial-engineering/financing) - Breakdown of program costs
- [UCLA Fees](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/degrees/master-of-financial-engineering/mfe-admit-central/program-calendar-and-fees#tab-fall-quarter-2024) - Official fee information and Payment Deadlines

### Financial Aid
- [UCLA Financial Aid Office](https://www.financialaid.ucla.edu/) - Information on grants, loans, and work-study
- [Non-UCLA Scholarships](https://www.scholarshipcenter.ucla.edu/scholarship-search/outside-scholarships/#othergraduate) - 3rd party scholarships
- [FAFSA Application](https://studentaid.gov/h/apply-for-aid/fafsa) - Apply for federal financial aid

### Student Employment
- [UCLA Career Center](https://www.asucla.ucla.edu/get-a-job) - Job listings for students
- [Work-Study Opportunities](https://financialaid.ucla.edu/types-of-aid/work-study) - Information on federal work-study
- [Handshake](https://ucla.joinhandshake.com/) - UCLA's job and internship platform

## Career Services {#career-services}

:::{.ucla-accent}
Prepare for your future career with job resources, networking opportunities, and professional development.
:::

### Job & Internship Resources
- [MFE Career Services](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/degrees/master-of-financial-engineering/career-impact) - MFE-specific career support
- [Anderson Career Services](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/career-services) - Career resources for Anderson students
- [Parker Career Management Center](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/parker) - Career development resources

### Networking
- [UCLA Alumni Association](https://alumni.ucla.edu/) - Connect with UCLA alumni
- [Financial Engineering Network](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/degrees/master-of-financial-engineering/student-experience) - MFE alumni network
- [LinkedIn UCLA Groups](https://www.linkedin.com/school/ucla/people/) - UCLA groups on LinkedIn

### Professional Development
- [Resume & Cover Letter Resources](https://www.career.ucla.edu/resume-and-cover-letters) - Templates and guides
- [Interview Preparation](https://www.career.ucla.edu/interviewing) - Interview tips and practice
- [Leadership Development](https://www.ucla.edu/student-life/leadership) - Leadership opportunities

## Student Life {#student-life}

:::{.ucla-accent}
Get involved in campus activities, join student organizations, and enjoy what UCLA has to offer.
:::

### Student Organizations
- [Anderson Student Association](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/mba-programs/full-time-mba/student-life/student-organizations) - Student clubs and organizations
- [Graduate Student Association](https://gsa.asucla.ucla.edu/) - Organization for graduate students
- [International Student Association](https://community.ucla.edu/studentorgs/international-students) - Support for international students. ch

### Campus Events
- [UCLA Central Calendar](https://www.ucla.edu/events) - University-wide events
- [Anderson Events](https://www.anderson.ucla.edu/events) - School-specific events
- [UCLA Recreation](https://www.recreation.ucla.edu/calendar) - Recreational activities and events

### Food & Dining
- [UCLA Dining Services](https://menu.dining.ucla.edu/hours) - Campus dining options
- [BruinCard Restaurants](https://bruincard.ucla.edu/where-use) - Places that accept BruinCard
- [Westwood Village Dining](https://www.experiencewestwood.com/dine) - Nearby restaurant options

## Health & Wellness {#health-wellness}

:::{.ucla-accent}
Take care of your physical and mental health with these essential wellness resources.
:::

### Medical Services
- [UCLA Arthur Ashe Student Health Center](https://www.studenthealth.ucla.edu/) - Primary care and specialty services
- [Student Health Insurance](https://www.studenthealth.ucla.edu/insurance) - Information on UCLA SHIP
- [COVID-19 Resources](https://covid-19.ucla.edu/) - Latest updates and protocols

### Mental Health Resources
- [Counseling and Psychological Services (CAPS)](https://www.counseling.ucla.edu/) - Mental health services
- [CAPS Workshops](https://www.counseling.ucla.edu/services/workshops) - Group therapy and workshops
- [Crisis Resources](https://www.counseling.ucla.edu/emergency-information) - Urgent mental health support

### Wellness Programs
- [UCLA Recreation](https://www.recreation.ucla.edu/) - Fitness centers and classes
- [Mindful Awareness Research Center](https://www.uclahealth.org/marc/) - Mindfulness resources
- [Healthy Campus Initiative](https://healthy.ucla.edu/) - Wellness programs and events

## Housing & Transportation {#housing-transportation}

:::{.ucla-accent}
Find housing options and navigate transportation to and around campus.
:::

### On-Campus Housing
- [UCLA Graduate Housing](https://housing.ucla.edu/my-housing/graduate-students-and-students-with-families) - Options for graduate students
- [Housing Application](https://portal.housing.ucla.edu/) - Apply for on-campus housing
- [Family Housing](https://housing.ucla.edu/my-housing/graduate-students-and-students-with-families/family-housing) - Options for students with families

### Off-Campus Housing
- [UCLA Community Housing Office](https://www.cho.ucla.edu/) - Off-campus housing resources
- [UCLA Rental Listings](https://www.cho.ucla.edu/housing-options/rental-listings) - Available apartments and roommates
- [Westwood Rentals Guide](https://www.cho.ucla.edu/housing-options/westwood-rentals) - Local rental information

### Transportation & Parking
- [UCLA Transportation](https://www.transportation.ucla.edu/) - Parking, transit, and alternative transportation
- [BruinBus](https://www.transportation.ucla.edu/campus-transit/bruinbus) - Campus shuttle service
- [Public Transit Information](https://www.transportation.ucla.edu/getting-to-ucla/public-transit) - Bus and metro options

